edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.service_garage

Class ServiceBay

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.service_garage.ServiceBay
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HybridElectricBay

    public class ServiceBay
extends java.lang.Object
    Concrete class representing service bay in the garage. Service bays can be regular or hybrid/electric. Regular can service any vehicle type while hybrid can service only hybrid or electric vehicles. A service bay has an id, empty of the vehicle. Uses custom array based list of service bays.
    Author:
    Summer Mims

      • ServiceBay

        public ServiceBay(java.lang.String prefix)
        Constructs a new ServiceBay object. Creates new empty service bay according to current bay numbering then increments that number. The prefix is determined by the user.
        Parameters:
        prefix - the first non whitespace character for the service bay name prefix

      • ServiceBay

        public ServiceBay()
        Constructs a new ServiceBay object. Creates new empty service bay according to current bay numbering then increments that number. The prefix is "1".
